National Fuel names new exploration chief . National Fuel Gas Co said Wednesday James A . Beck has been elected president of Seneca Resources Corp , its Houston - based natural gas and oil exploration and production subsidiary . He was executive vice president . Beck replaces Philip C . Ackerman who is also President of National Fuel ' s utility and senior vice president of National Fuel Gas , the company said . - - New York Newsdesk 212 - 859 - 1610 . 
